      "id": "REQ-0021",
      "kind": "Functional",
      "links": [],
      "priority": "Should",
      "rationale": "History without an actor is half-useful; pulling from standard environment variables avoids requiring config while still attributing changes.",
      "statement": "The system shall determine the current actor from REQ_ACTOR, USER or USERNAME in that order and shall record the resolved value on each history entry.",
      "status": "Implemented",
      "tags": [
